---
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto my-12 p-8 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="text-center mb-10 relative z-10">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy">Local Assessment Pathway</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Available for families in Lahore, Pakistan.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10">
    <!-- Connecting line for desktop -->
    <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-brand-sky -translate-y-1/2 z-0"></div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg border-2 border-brand-trust text-center shadow-sm relative z-10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
        <div class="text-brand-trust font-bold text-sm uppercase mb-2">Step 1</div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800">Initial Intake</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">Parent interview and history collection</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-center shadow-sm relative z-10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
        <div class="text-brand-navy font-bold text-sm uppercase mb-2">Step 2</div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800">Testing</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">Standardized clinical assessment tools</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-center shadow-sm relative z-10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
        <div class="text-brand-navy font-bold text-sm uppercase mb-2">Step 3</div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800">Analysis</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">Scoring and comprehensive report writing</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-brand-navy text-white p-5 rounded-lg border border-brand-navy text-center shadow-md relative z-10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
        <div class="text-brand-sky font-bold text-sm uppercase mb-2">Step 4</div>
        <h4 class="font-bold">Feedback</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-brand-cream mt-2">Results discussion and action plan</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
